title: Hay House World Summit 2013
description:
All 110 talks from this 10-days summit, that took place at the beginning of June. Over 110 hours of inspiring conversations from favorite teachers (duration of individual clips ranges from 44 to 78 minutes). For more information please visit http://www.hayhouseworldsummit.com

Audio properties: 128 kbps, stereo, 44.1 KHz (with rare exceptions of 22 KHz)

All clips are IDv3 tagged for your convenience.

Enjoy!
